name: 365force Inc.
overview:
365force is a provider of cloud technology, cloud strategy and cloud consulting. To support these we provide cloud infrastructure and Cloud Processed Outsourcing (CPO) services. Our focus is on innovation and know-how. We provide local and vertical industry expertise drawn from our worldwide resources to work together with clients to help make their businesses grow.

Global Cloud Platform: Outsourcing is now a strategic directive for companies worldwide that want to remain competitive in a the dynamic and challenging global economy.

365force can help you create a new source of business value by providing in-depth industry and strategy expertise, combined with technologically innovative solutions that are rapidly executed and will give you a return on your investment.
